and the form of the partial-fraction expansion that results is

\[G(\nu)\,=\,\sum_{i\,=\,1}^{r}\sum_{k\,=\,1}^{\sigma_{i}}\frac{B_{ik}}{(1-\rho _{i}^{-1}\nu)^{k}}.\] (A.58)

